OAK KNOLL VILLAGE CONDOMINIUM OWNERS ASSOCIATION, Plaintiff,
v.
Chris Ann JAYE, Defendant-Petitioner. C-876 September Term 2018
082210 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 14, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004942-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
